---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact AutomatorLabs | Bugs, Ideas, and Feedback"
  description="Contact AutomatorLabs to report a calculator bug, suggest a financial calculator or guide, or share general feedback."
>
  <main id="main-content">
    <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li aria-current="page">Contact</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <header class="page-header">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
      <h1>Questions, ideas, or something not adding up?</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        AutomatorLabs welcomes clear, practical feedback about its free
        calculators and educational guides.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="contact-grid">
      <section aria-labelledby="bug-heading">
        <h2 id="bug-heading">Report a calculator bug</h2>
        <p>
          If a result looks incorrect or a calculator does not behave as
          expected, open a GitHub issue. Include the calculator URL, the inputs
          used, the result shown, and what you expected instead. Avoid including
          sensitive personal or financial information.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/AutomatorLabs/automatorlabs-seo-machine/issues/new"
        >
          Report a bug on GitHub
        </a>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="suggestion-heading">
        <h2 id="suggestion-heading">Suggest a calculator or guide</h2>
        <p>
          Suggestions are useful when they describe the question the tool
          should answer, the inputs it would need, and the result that would
          help users make sense of the topic.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/AutomatorLabs/automatorlabs-seo-machine/issues/new"
        >
          Share a suggestion
        </a>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="general-heading">
        <h2 id="general-heading">General contact</h2>
        <p>
          For other project feedback, documentation corrections, or questions
          about the site, visit the AutomatorLabs repository and open an issue
          with a concise description.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/AutomatorLabs/automatorlabs-seo-machine">
          Visit the GitHub repository
        </a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    width: min(960px, calc(100% - 2rem));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 0 5rem;
  }

  .breadcrumbs {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--muted-text-color);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .breadcrumbs ol {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.45rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .breadcrumbs li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.45rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .breadcrumbs li + li::before {
    color: var(--muted-text-color);
    content: '›';
  }

  .breadcrumbs a,
  .contact-grid a {
    color: var(--link-color);
  }

  .breadcrumbs a {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .breadcrumbs a:hover,
  .contact-grid a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .breadcrumbs [aria-current='page'] {
    color: var(--text-color);
    font-weight: 650;
  }

  .page-header {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
    color: var(--link-color);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 7vw, 4rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .intro {
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    color: var(--muted-text-color);
    font-size: 1.12rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-grid section {
    display: flex;
    min-height: 100%;
    flex-direction: column;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 15px;
    background: var(--card-background);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px var(--shadow-color);
    padding: 1.4rem;
  }

  .contact-grid h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .contact-grid p {
    margin: 0.7rem 0 1.2rem;
    color: var(--muted-text-color);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-grid a {
    margin-top: auto;
    font-weight: 750;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    main {
      padding-top: 3rem;
    }

    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
